Company Overview of Saban Brands LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Saban Brands LLC acquires and develops a portfolio of consumer brands in the entertainment and lifestyle sectors worldwide. The company specializes in growing and monetizing entertainment and lifestyle brands through content, media, marketing, distribution, licensing, and retail to various markets worldwide and to consumers of various ages. It develops content that resonates with consumers across various media platforms; and acquires and grows brands that have a passionate consumer following and global reach. Saban Brands LLC was founded in 2010 and is based in Los Angeles, California. It has additional offices in Los Angeles, New York, London, and Sydney.


10100 Santa Monica BoulevardSuite 500Los Angeles, CA 90067United StatesFounded in 2010



Phone: 310-557-5230

Fax: 310-861-1597

www.sabanbrands.com







