Insider Activity


Individual




Thomas D. Saban



Dr. Thomas D. Saban is Independent Director at National American University Holdings, Inc. and Vice President-Administration & Finance at Prairie State College. He is on the Board of Directors at National American University Holdings, Inc.
Dr. Saban was previously employed as CFO, Vice President-Administration & Finance by Rocky Vista University, CFO, Vice President-Administration & Finance by Texas A&M University, an Associate Vice President-Planning & Budgets by St. Petersburg College, CFO, Vice President-Administration & Finance by Worcester State College, and CFO, Vice President-Administration & Finance by Chadron State College. He also served on the board at Camden Learning Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Wyoming, an MBA from the University of Miami (Florida), and a doctorate degree from Barry University.



